366
00:24:50,460 --> 00:24:51,050
Yes.

367
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,630
Touch my hair.

368
00:24:56,550 --> 00:24:57,140
Come on.

369
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:04,200
Rub it.

370
00:25:05,530 --> 00:25:06,970
Feel its texture.

371
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:13,520
Now touch my face.

372
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,400
Feel the texture of my skin.

373
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:52,770
Finished.

374
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:54,010
Congratulations.

375
00:26:06,290 --> 00:26:07,130
Let's take a photo.

376
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,480
Thank you for your hard work.

377
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,470
I'll make you some coffee.

378
00:26:31,130 --> 00:26:33,730
Lanxin, happy birthday.

379
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:40,930
Remember those feelings

380
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:42,730
and digest them slowly.

381
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:45,010
Then express them

382
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,840
fully through your sketching.

383
00:26:48,670 --> 00:26:50,020
That's the essence of portrait drawing.

384
00:26:56,090 --> 00:26:58,830
I don't know if it's the sun or you,

385
00:27:00,130 --> 00:27:01,950
but it's so dazzling I can't look directly.

386
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:12,480
What's wrong?

387
00:27:13,290 --> 00:27:15,310
I suddenly have a stomachache.

388
00:27:15,490 --> 00:27:16,530
I'll draw it another day.

389
00:27:17,190 --> 00:27:18,190
Luhui.

390
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,920
What are these feelings?

391
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:30,920
These feelings

392
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:33,840
are too much for me to draw.

393
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:37,870
Is this

394
00:27:38,770 --> 00:27:41,700
what it feels like to like someone?

395
00:27:55,450 --> 00:27:57,050
Do you feel anything now?

396
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,680
You should let Yu Xing know

397
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,690
how you feel about him.

398
00:27:59,940 --> 00:28:01,240
When will you be ready

399
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:02,940
to accept a new relationship?

400
00:28:03,490 --> 00:28:04,450
Did you

401
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:07,620
bring him to me?

402
00:28:09,490 --> 00:28:11,450
I just want you to know my feelings.

403
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,340
It's okay if you don't respond the same way.

404
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:17,320
Feel your own emotions.

405
00:28:18,090 --> 00:28:19,890
I thought you were here to see me.

406
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,300
I wasn't.
